# Agent worktrees. When committed these become orphan gitlinks (mode 160000 with no .gitmodules
# entry), which break recursive submodule traversal in the umbrella, see ADR 0004. Ten of them
# were committed here once already, referencing objects that never existed. They recur; keep
# them out of the index.
.claude/worktrees/
